title: United Kingdom Imports - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts & Plants Parts Prepared
description: Imports - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts & Plants Parts Prepared in the United Kingdom increased to 303.78 GBP Million in September from 297.68 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts & Plants Parts Pr in the United Kingdom averaged 168.69 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 326.90 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 69.44 GBP Million in February of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Vegetable, Fruit, Nuts & Plants Parts.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
